'''Cynthia Butare''', [[Rwanda|numunyarwanda]] - umukinnyi wa firime wu Busuwisi kimwe naba videwo<ref>https://www.newtimes.co.rw/lifestyle/cynthia-butare-her-long-journey-filmmaking</ref> .  Azwi cyane nk'umuyobozi wa firime ''Kickin 'It With The Kinks'' <ref>https://www.africatechsummit.com/kigali/cth_speaker/cynthia-butare/</ref>. 

== Ubuzima bwite ==
Yavukiye i Geneve mu [[Busuwisi]]. Yabaye i Geneve kugeza arangije amashuri yisumbuye hanyuma yimukira mu [[Bwongereza]] kwiga amashuri makuru<ref>https://www.tvguide.com/celebrities/cynthia-butare/3030107825/</ref>. 

== Umwuga ==
Yabonye impamyabumenyi ihanitse muri Digital Media and Communication nyuma arangiza Master's in Documentary Practice muri kaminuza ya Manchester Metropolitan<ref>http://www.spla.pro/file.person.cynthia-umulisa-butare.49771.html</ref> .  Muri 2011, yakoze ''Kickin 'It With The Kinks'' kumushinga wa kaminuza. Filime yakira igihembo cya documentaire nziza mu ishami rye.<ref>https://www.vsual.co/shop/cynthia-butare</ref> Nyuma mu 2016, Cynthia ari kumwe n'inshuti ye Mundia, bahisemo gukora verisiyo ndende ya firime.  Iyi filime yakiriwe neza kandi yerekanwa mu birori mpuzamahanga bya firime.  Muri uwo mwaka, yatangije isosiyete ye bwite, 'CB Production'<ref>https://chroniquebeautenoire.com/cynthia-butare-capture-grace/</ref>. 

Akiri ingimbi, yatangiye kwandika mu 2003. Nubwo yahagaritse kwandika nyuma yimyaka itatu, yatangiye blog 2012. Muri 2013, Butare yahawe igihembo cya Blog nziza yumwaka na BEFFTA. Icyakora, yimukiye mu [[Rwanda]] mu 2014.<ref>https://eclipsetheatre.org.uk/whats-on/1225-kickin--it-with-the-kinks---2105-sheffield-film-screening</ref>  Igihe yari mu [[Rwanda]], yakoze filime ye ya kabiri ya documentaire, ''Ishimwa: Kuva Amaraso Yera Kuri Grace'' . Yerekanwe mu rwego rwo kwerekana iserukiramuco rya sinema mu [[Rwanda]]. Kuri ubu arimo gukora umushinga witwa ''The Return''<ref>https://rwanda.shafaqna.com/EN/AL/231517</ref> . 

